    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(L) In nomine domini nostri Iehsu Christi eterni Dei amen, anno nativitate
                        eius millesimo centesimo optuaesimo primo, pridie idus setembris, indictione
                        quintadecima. Ex huius instrumenti pateat recitatione quod nos, <persName
                            ref="#people/3226">Castracanis</persName> quondam <persName
                            ref="#people/3214">Uberti</persName> et <persName><name ref="Castraleo"
                                >Castraleo</name></persName> filius eius, (…) ambo simul
                        irrevocabiliter pro animarum nostrarum remedio donamus et tradimus vobis
                                <persName><name ref="Aldebrandus">Aldibrandino</name></persName>
                        camerario et <persName><name ref="Aldus">Aldinello</name></persName> hospiti
                        peregrinorum fratribus <orgName key="#Hospitals"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3206"><rs key="#Hospitals">hospitalis</rs>
                            <placeName ref="#places/3207" key="#Hospitals"
                            >Altepascensis</placeName></orgName>, recipientibus pro <persName><name
                                ref="Dominicus">Dominico</name></persName> rectore (…) medietatem
                        integram pro indiviso unius nostre terre petie, que est posita in loco et
                        finibus <placeName ref="#places/3210" key="#Rivers #Roads">Putei</placeName>
                        et olim recta fuit per <persName><name ref="Albonectus"
                            >Albonettum</name></persName> magistrum. Que vero tenet unum caput in
                            <rs key="#Roads">via publica</rs>, aliud in <rs key="#Rivers">flumine
                            Iussiana</rs>, unum laterum tenet in terra que detinent filii quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Folcardus">Folcardini</name></persName>, aliud
                        in terra que detinet <persName><name ref="Rodelandus"
                            >Rolandinus</name></persName> quondam ***. <foreign>Pena</foreign>: in
                        duplum. (…) Actum apud Puteum et in domo <persName><name ref="Bernardus"
                                >Bernardi</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Widuccius"
                                >Guiducii</name></persName>. (…) <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Fracassus">Fracassus</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Bernardus">Bernardi</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Iacobus">Iacop</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Widoloctus">Guidalotti</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Mezzovillano">Methovillanus</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Robertus">Rubertini</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Hugolinus"
                            >Ugolinus</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Petrus"
                                >Petri</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Molestus">Molestus</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Iohannes">Iohannis</name></persName> suprascripti rogati <rs
                            key="#Witness">testes</rs> interfuerunt. (L) Ego <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Leonardus">Leonardus</name></persName>
                        domni imperatoris <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> post traditam <rs
                            key="#Writer">scripsi</rs>, complevi et dedi. </ab>
                </div>
